belt and assist patients in ambulation. \n- Analyze the patient's condition and environment to adjust the approach as needed. \n- Evaluate their technique to ensure it adheres to best practices and safety standards. \n- Create a safe and supportive environment for patients during ambulation using a transfer belt. \n\nThis comprehensive approach ensures CNAs are well-prepared to assist patients with proper care efficiently and compassionately in real-world clinical settings. ", "short_description": "Learn the essential skill of safely assisting patients to ambulate using a transfer belt."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Holo Pundits", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1043107547362485"}, {"id": "478089301798119"}, {"id": "514087707868786"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7956572267762275"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "477867771836880"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "477867771836880"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1725450000, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "477867771836880"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "87182647